short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Use the Vercel Toolbar on production deployments

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Installing this extension allows you to use the Vercel Toolbar on your production Vercel deployments & unlocks an easy-to-use feature for taking screenshots when commenting on all of your Vercel deployments.
